{
  "info": {
    "name": "MG Plastic — Notifications (Plumber + Trader)",
    "_postman_id": "e9f0a1b2-notif-4000-9000-mgnotifinbox",
    "description": "# إشعارات الموبايل (قاعدة البيانات)\n\nتخزين Laravel: جدول `notifications` (UUID) مربوط بالمستخدم (`notifiable`).\n\n## مسارات متكافئة\nنفس الـ API متاح على:\n- `/api/v1/mobile/notifications/*` (أي دور بعد login)\n- `/api/v1/mobile/plumber/notifications/*`\n- `/api/v1/mobile/trader/notifications/*`\n\n## العمليات\n| Method | Path | معنى |\n|--------|------|------|\n| GET | `/` | قائمة + pagination + summary |\n| GET | `/summary` | total / unread / read |\n| GET | `/unread-count` | عداد غير المقروء |\n| GET | `/{id}` | تفاصيل إشعار |\n| POST | `/{id}/read` | تعليم مقروء |\n| POST | `/{id}/unread` | تعليم غير مقروء |\n| POST | `/read-all` | الكل مقروء |\n| POST | `/read-many` | `{ids:[...]}` |\n| DELETE | `/{id}` | حذف واحد |\n| POST | `/delete-many` | `{ids:[...]}` |\n| DELETE | `/read` | حذف المقروء فقط |\n| DELETE | `/` | حذف الكل |\n\n### Query على القائمة\n`per_page`, `page`, `filter=unread|read`, `unread_only=1`, `read_only=1`, `status=info|success|warning|danger`, `q=`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://mg-plastic.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_phone", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_password", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "plumber_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "trader_phone", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "trader_password", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "trader_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "notification_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "per_page", "value": "20", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 — Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Plumber",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "type": "text/javascript",
              "exec": [
                "const json = pm.response.json();",
                "const token = json?.data?.token || json?.token;",
                "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('plumber_token', token);"
              ]
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{plumber_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{plumber_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Trader",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "type": "text/javascript",
              "exec": [
                "const json = pm.response.json();",
